Q: What is liberation?
<br>A: In simple words: freedom from thoughts is liberation. The bondage is due to our thoughts. When that thought process is stopped, a higher consciousness develops, and that higher consciousness is the cause of liberation.
<br>Q: Are our thoughts valuable?
<br>A: In the beginning, positive thoughts are the foundation. But after attaining higher consciousness, you don&#8217;t need any thoughts. <span class=date>9/10/78</span>
